<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="97">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="97">The type material at B was destroyed during World War II. I am selecting as the lectotype the duplicate preserved at US that I have studied. I have also seen the duplicate at G, but have not carefully studied it.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="97">
